Savedis - Open Source Mini Bookmarking Tool 
-----------------------------------------------------------

Author: Serdar Yildirim // me[dot]serdaryildirim[dot]com
Website: savedis.com
Demo Website: savedis.com
Current Version: 0.9

Started as a Rails 3 learning app.

Current Features
-----------------------------------------------------------

* Public / Private bookmark management
* Public / Private note management
* Personal bookmark title and comment
* Tagging bookmarks and notes
* Registration / Login
* User profiles with public bookmarks and notes

Dependencies
-----------------------------------------------------------

* ruby >= 1.9.2
* rubygems >= 1.3.7
* ruby on rails 3

Installation
-----------------------------------------------------------

* Install the dependencies
	sudo gem install bundler
	
* Download savedis source code
	https://github.com/serdary/savedis
	
* Change the application configs
	config/config.yml
	config/database.yml
	
* Install app dependencies
	bundle install

* Start the server
	rails s
	